<text>主张实行胎教，对儿童及早教育。</text>
<is_italic>false</is_italic>
<is_bold>false</is_bold>
</rich_text_item>
</richText>
<richText type="complextext"><rich_text_item type="text_type_begin_tool1">
<text_indent>40</text_indent>
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_text_tool1">
<font_color>#444444</font_color>
<font_size>20</font_size>
<font_family>Palatino</font_family>
<text>留下名作《颜世家训》，提倡及早施教、以身作则、严慈相济、一视同仁等儿童家庭教育主张。</text>
<is_italic>false</is_italic>
<is_bold>false</is_bold>
</rich_text_item>
</richText>
<richText type="complextext"><rich_text_item type="text_type_begin_tool1">
<text_indent>40</text_indent>
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_text_tool1">
<font_color>#444444</font_color>
<font_size>20</font_size>
<font_family>Palatino</font_family>
<text>编写了《童蒙须知》，主张小学“学其事”，通过格言、故事等教给儿童道德观念，学习基本行为规范。</text>
<is_italic>false</is_italic>
<is_bold>false</is_bold>
</rich_text_item>
</richText>
<richText type="complextext"><rich_text_item type="text_type_begin_tool1">
<text_indent>40</text_indent>
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_text_tool1">
<font_color>#444444</font_color>
<font_size>20</font_size>
<font_family>Palatino</font_family>
<text>对压抑儿童的传统教育方法提出批判，主张儿童教育要顺应童子之情，倡导以生动活泼的方法教儿童，歌诗、习礼、读书是儿童学习的内容。</text>
<is_italic>false</is_italic>
<is_bold>false</is_bold>
